QuestData.Title: Iron Low Tide
QuestData.Description:
A few years ago I tried to join the Irontide. They said I wasn't "Irontide material", not cruel or heartless enough!
So I teamed up with Nedly and Moxie here in Deadwash, and we started looking for treasure on our own.
Let's show these Irontide they're not "Deadwash material".
QuestData.CompletionText: Show the Irontide they aren't tough enough to hang around here!
QuestData.RewardText: No one's gonna cry about a few less pirates. I may even dance about it!
